Following link was got from the dockerfile of nexus.
Reference: https://github.com/sonatype/docker-nexus3

wget -O /tmp/nexus.tar.gz https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.30.1-01-unix.tar.gz


cd /etc/docker/daemon.json

